description: Under normal market conditions, the fund invests at least 80% of its net assets, plus borrowings for investment purposes, if any, in equity securities of issuers located in emerging markets countries that, at the time of investment, meet the environmental, social, and governance (ESG) criteria established by Emerge Capital Management Inc. (Emerge or the Advisor). It invests predominantly in equity securities. The fund is non-diversified.
name: Emerge EMPWR Sustainable Emerging Markets Equity ETF
